item.title: EP 21 - Move Dem Bones
item.itunes:title: Move Dem Bones
item.description:
Today we look at delusional pet owners, the science of erectile dysfunction, and giant sea creatures!

Patreon 

https://www.patreon.com/user?u=18482113

MERCH STORE!!!
https://tinyurl.com/y8zam4o2

A recent survey showed that 50% of British men in their 30s suffer from erectile dysfunction. The men blame it on issues like stress or drinking. But are those the right reasons, or is there something else that is making men lose the battle of the bulge?

Then we take a chilly dive into the coldest oceans of the world where we learn the colder the water, the bigger the beast!

And lastly, we get a report of a man who believe his dog is a synthetic life form sent to spy on him on behalf of an army of clones. So, yeah, we take the train to Crazy Town this episode.
